'''自治市公園'''（{{lang-en|Borough Park}}）是美国[[纽约市|纽约市]][[布鲁克林区|布鲁克林区]]西南部的一个社区，南到本森赫斯特，西南到湾脊區，西到[[日落公园|日落公园]]，东北到肯辛顿，东到[[夫拉特布什|夫拉特布什]]，东南到米德伍德。

菠萝园是以色列以外最大的[[犹太教正统派|犹太教正统派]]社区之一，是美国最大的犹太人集中地之一。由于[[哈西迪犹太教|哈西迪犹太教]]和[[哈雷迪犹太教|哈雷迪犹太教]]家庭中的平均儿童数是6.72，菠萝园正在经历人口急剧增长。<ref>Marvin Schick. [http://www.simpletoremember.com/vitals/will-your-grandchild-be-jewish-chart-graph.htm "A Census of Jewish Day Schools in The United States."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.simpletoremember.com/vitals/will-your-grandchild-be-jewish-chart-graph.htm |date=20201209224708 }}</ref>它是一个经济多样化的社区。<ref name = "Orthodox Neighborhood Reshapes Itself">Sontag, Deborah. "[http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9802E7DD1030F934A35752C0A96E958260 Orthodox Neighborhood Reshapes Itself] {{Wayback|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9802E7DD1030F934A35752C0A96E958260 |date=20200601041456 }}." ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]''. January 7, 1998. pg. A1.</ref>

